description: Seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the S&P 500 Scored & Screened IndexEFIV is designed to track an index that is designed to select S&P 500 firms meeting certain sustainability criteria (criteria related to environmental, social and governance factors) while maintaining similar overall industry group weights as the S&P 500 IndexEFIV may serve as a potential ESG core exposure, based on its focus on sustainability criteria and comprehensive market coverage of the flagship core S&P 500 Index
name: SPDR S&P 500 ESG ETF
